<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧小声地哭着：“悟空是对的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些善良的村民原来都是妖怪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他被绳子绑在一根柱子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净也被绑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该听悟空的话。”悟净一边说一边努力挣脱绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒扭动着身子大喊：“妖怪！可恶的妖怪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们竟敢抓我们！你们会后悔的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空是齐天大圣孙悟空！连玉皇大帝都害怕的孙悟空！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会来救我们的！你们就等着吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，八戒的肚子咕咕叫了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱了皱眉：“八戒，你怎么现在还想着吃呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净摇了摇头：“过分了，八戒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也没办法呀。” 八戒继续扭动，“我今天什么都没吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看着八戒和悟净扭来扭去：“那样有用吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声：“我的绳子松了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒的喊声在山洞里回荡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨房里的几个小妖听到后，跑去找他们的大王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王瞪了他们一眼：“你们在做什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要饿死了！怎么还不做唐僧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小妖端着一碗香料：“大王，我们正准备做唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我们抓来的人认识孙悟空，齐天大圣孙悟空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王打了个哈欠：“嗯，我也听到了那头猪在大叫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那怎么办？” 那个小妖问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空很厉害。他打败了所有天兵天将！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“连玉皇大帝也害怕他！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要是吃了唐僧，孙悟空一定会打死我们。” 另一个小妖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个小妖浑身发抖：“也许我们不应该吃唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王抬起一只手：“我们要吃了唐僧，那样就能长生不老。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不怕孙悟空。迅翼知道一个人能帮我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边的迅翼大吃一惊：“您说我知道？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王点了点头：“你说看到了一个比孙悟空还厉害的女神仙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小妖大吃一惊，手上拿的碗掉在了地上：“比孙悟空还厉害？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小妖们期待地看着迅翼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女神仙在哪儿，迅翼？”黑雨大王问，“我想见见她。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……您见不到她。” 迅翼说，“她在另一个世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王站了起来：“你一定知道怎么去那里。快告诉我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅翼抖着身子飞快地念出咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光芒四射，然后——咻！出现了一个图像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>图像里是个有很多高楼的奇怪王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“女神仙就在那里。” 迅翼小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太神奇了！” 黑雨大王低声说，“这个图像看起来很真实。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是真的。” 迅翼叹了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咒语打开了通向另一个世界的传送门，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要穿过那道门，就会到达那个世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！一扇门炸开了，八戒冲了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会让你们伤害我师父……啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒被地上的碗绊了一下，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>直接滚进了传送门，门在他身后消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咻！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>